          "datePublished": "2024-06-15",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "3",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Currently I am studying in St. theresa senior secondary school. I am studying here since 2015 from my 2nd grade and till now I have only participated in one dance show in my 5th class. This school is good but in the name extra curricular activities only limited students have access to do extra curricular activities I have seen only 4-5 students doing extra curricular activities all these years and now i can't hope more from this school because it's nearly the end time of my studies but  this shouldn't be happening with my juniors!!! Dear St theresa please give more opportunities to all the students no one should be given privileges for specific things otherwise the study system is okay . The only problem is there is very less extra curricular activities.\n\nAs I have seen other school students they all participate in various type of activities competitions out of school with very different different students but in my school I can only see 3-4 faces that are doing various competitions and activities. Everyone should be treated equally!!",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
